  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2> European Luxury Holidays for 2025</h2>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13098866/hotel-post-ischgl-aussenpool-1-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Luxury Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/18902519ede441bdb30b57e956cebf59" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/aed5ab65747f4034a4453aa23eefc6da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aed5ab65747f4034a4453aa23eefc6da}" title="Hotel Post">Image: Hotel Post, Ischgl</a></p>
<p>Dive into a sea of relaxation with our European luxury summer holidays, where your well-being takes center stage. Think top-end rooms, exceptional dining and rejuvenating spas.</p>
<p>Sure, boots were made for walking, but your feet deserve some pampering too. After conquering the trails and sights, treat your feet to well-deserved relaxation at some of the best European spa hotels.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">What Makes an Inghams Luxury Holiday?</h2>
<p> </p>
