<h3>Beautiful Destinations</h3>
<div class="c-card__header"></div>
<p><span>Discover Europe’s breathtaking destinations, from Italy's lakes to the alpine wonders of Chamonix, Switzerland, and the timeless beauty of Austria.</span></p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/f23d2b62232e4404a3831a9510eff1e0" href="#destination" class="c-btn" data-anchor="#destination">Our Destinations</a></p>
