<h3>Seamless Escapes</h3>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><span>Flights, transfers and accommodation are included on all our holidays. We take care of the small details so you don’t have to. </span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/1e437ab1de9c402abf63da580ffe1715" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e437ab1de9c402abf63da580ffe1715}" title="About Us" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
